room_title: Escape room "Mastaba" by Waco Escape Rooms in Waco
room_description:
Scattered across the state, people have been going missing for years. Rumors swirl about runaways, madness, and dark figures lurking in shadows. The truth? There's a predator on the prowl, stalking and selecting the fittest among us. And you are about to join their number.
Only 60 minutes remain until Mastaba returns and finishes what he started. Will you escape, or will you join his collection permanently?
